---
layout: base
title: Newsletter
description: Subscribe to The Freethinking Times, independent journalism delivered directly to your inbox.
permalink: /newsletter/
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: var(--space-16); padding-bottom: var(--space-24);">

  {# ── Hero ── #}
  <header style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-16); text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-masthead); font-size: var(--text-3xl); line-height: var(--leading-tight); margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">One email, one article.</h1>
    <p style="font-size: var(--text-lg); color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-loose);">
      Every piece we publish &mdash; investigative, philosophical, adversarial to power &mdash; delivered the moment it goes live. No algorithms deciding what you see. No weekly digest burying the work. The piece, when it&rsquo;s ready.
    </p>
  </header>

  {# ── Sign-up form ── #}
  <div style="max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-20);">
    <form class="subscribe-form subscribe-form--stacked" novalidate>
      <label for="subscribe-email-newsletter" class="visually-hidden">Your email address</label>
      <input
        class="subscribe-form__input"
        id="subscribe-email-newsletter"
        type="email"
        name="email"
        placeholder="your@email.com"
        autocomplete="email"
        required>
      <button class="subscribe-form__btn" type="submit">Subscribe</button>
    </form>
    <div class="subscribe-status" role="alert" aria-live="polite"></div>
    <p style="font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-ink-faint); text-align: center; margin-top: var(--space-4); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);">
      Free. Unsubscribe anytime. We don&rsquo;t share your address. <a href="/privacy/" style="color: var(--color-ink-faint);">Privacy policy</a>.
    </p>
  </div>

  {# ── What you get ── #}
  <div style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-16);">
    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule); margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-masthead); font-size: var(--text-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">What to expect</h2>
    <dl style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-8);">
      <div>
        <dt style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">One email per article</dt>
        <dd style="color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-loose);">We publish when we have something worth publishing, not on a quota. Each email carries one piece, fully readable in your inbox if you prefer it that way.</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Every section, every subject</dt>
        <dd style="color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-loose);">News, opinion, analysis, history, science, arts and culture, whatever we publish, you'll receive. No section is hidden behind a separate list.</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">No tracking pixels, no click surveillance</dt>
        <dd style="color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-loose);">Open tracking and click tracking are disabled. We don't monitor your reading behaviour inside the email. Links include a UTM tag so our site analytics can attribute traffic to the newsletter in aggregate, nothing more.</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Powered by Buttondown</dt>
        <dd style="color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-loose);">We use <a href="https://buttondown.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Buttondown</a>, an independent newsletter platform. Your email address is stored on their servers and governed by <a href="https://buttondown.com/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">their privacy policy</a>.</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>

  {# ── Past issues ── #}
  <div style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-16);">
    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule); margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-masthead); font-size: var(--text-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Past issues</h2>
    <p style="color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-loose); margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">
      Every issue is archived and publicly readable. Browse before you subscribe.
    </p>
    <a href="https://buttondown.com/{{ site.newsletter.username }}/archive" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-link);">View the full archive &rarr;</a>
  </div>

  {# ── From the archive: a surfacing affordance for older pieces.
     Pulls the three oldest articles as a 'worth revisiting' strip; no
     backend change needed. Over time this becomes a built-in rediscovery
     tool alongside the forward-looking feed. ── #}
  {# Oldest pieces first — collections.allContent is sorted chronologically,
     so the head of the list is the furthest back. Those are the ones
     least likely to surface on their own. #}
  {% set archiveSurface = collections.allContent | limit(3) %}
  {% if archiveSurface.length %}
  <div class="nl-archive-surface">
    <hr class="divider" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
    <div class="nl-archive-surface__header">
      <p class="nl-archive-surface__kicker">From the archive</p>
      <h2 class="nl-archive-surface__title">Pieces worth revisiting</h2>
      <p class="nl-archive-surface__lede">
        A rotating surface of older work. The feed goes forward; the archive stays available.
      </p>
    </div>
    <ul class="nl-archive-surface__list">
      {% for item in archiveSurface %}
      <li class="nl-archive-surface__item">
        <a href="{{ item.url }}" class="nl-archive-surface__link">
          {% if item.data.section %}<span class="nl-archive-surface__section">{{ item.data.section }}</span>{% endif %}
          <span class="nl-archive-surface__headline">{{ item.data.title }}</span>
          <span class="nl-archive-surface__meta">
            {% if item.data.author and authors[item.data.author] %}{{ authors[item.data.author].name }} &middot; {% endif %}{{ item.data.date | readableDate }}
          </span>
        </a>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    <p class="nl-archive-surface__footnote">
      <a href="/archives/">Browse the full archive &rarr;</a>
    </p>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <style>
  .nl-archive-surface {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-16);
  }
  .nl-archive-surface__header { margin-bottom: var(--space-6); }
  .nl-archive-surface__kicker {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2);
  }
  .nl-archive-surface__title {
    font-family: var(--font-masthead, var(--font-headline));
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
  }
  .nl-archive-surface__lede {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3);
  }
  .nl-archive-surface__list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-5);
  }
  .nl-archive-surface__link {
    display: block;
    padding: var(--space-4) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background var(--transition-fast);
  }
  .nl-archive-surface__item:last-child .nl-archive-surface__link { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-rule); }
  .nl-archive-surface__link:hover { background: var(--color-bg-alt); }
  .nl-archive-surface__section {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.66rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .nl-archive-surface__headline {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-headline);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-size: var(--text-md);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
  }
  .nl-archive-surface__link:hover .nl-archive-surface__headline { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .nl-archive-surface__meta {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-ink-faint);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .nl-archive-surface__footnote {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .nl-archive-surface__footnote a { color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 600; }
  </style>

  {# ── Other ways to follow ── #}
  <div style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule); margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-masthead); font-size: var(--text-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">Other ways to follow</h2>
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr)); gap: var(--space-4);">
      <a href="/feed.xml" style="display: block; padding: var(--space-5); border: 1px solid var(--color-rule); border-radius: var(--radius-md); text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-ink);">
        <p style="font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">RSS Feed</p>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-normal);">Subscribe in any RSS reader.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/reading-list/" style="display: block; padding: var(--space-5); border: 1px solid var(--color-rule); border-radius: var(--radius-md); text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-ink);">
        <p style="font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Reading List</p>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-normal);">Bookmark articles to read later.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/editions/" style="display: block; padding: var(--space-5); border: 1px solid var(--color-rule); border-radius: var(--radius-md); text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-ink);">
        <p style="font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Editions</p>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-normal);">Browse the publication by edition.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
